{"tid":2032264,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"到底香港人做緊咩？ 香港發生咩事？ 同我入黎睇哩張meme","createTime":"2020-05-24T03:27:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T15:32:56.000Z","uid":16025,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"43c21bb2f25c39c59c2139a3ba1b6a2ddc2608e2","tid":2032264,"uid":16025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:27:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TCDGXCk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTCDGXCk.png&h=1a88c055&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿煲用左丹麥@Succespictures 二次創作meme<br />\n<br />\n清晰話俾全世界聽，就算CCP攬炒香港，我地都唔會放棄，浴火重生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時代革命，重光抗爭<br />\n<br />\n香港民族，唯一出路<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c02fc1cd8ddcad00f4efc7effecd28533cd2048e","tid":2032264,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:28:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好貼切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"cbe12cbefd0371f25a7b428086fbdf7437a80089","tid":2032264,"uid":16025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:33:38.000Z","msg":"push!岩用就幫手SHARE 出去"},{"pid":"947288613aa921a2fffad67bc8e07ac27b0235ff","tid":2032264,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69fd91891e071254d7fad895951d7ebf18b21321","tid":2032264,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:36:03.000Z","msg":"推埋上Twitter啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位，連登黑色五毛風向警告</span><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n再借個位<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n最後想請大家簽一簽以下聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtQHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=ee6b18ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"6f3d8c5924d63119dfb910f31d3feabe6091bde2","tid":2032264,"uid":16025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:36:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"96f6c91421e22ca65accc4c5734ef609763e25d6","tid":2032264,"uid":177955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:37:10.000Z","msg":"ok嘅 但係呢個係政治漫畫多過meme<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97532d8